    "description": "《Sokobond Express》是一款精美的极简解谜游戏，本作以新颖的方式将化学键合与路径解谜相结合，为您奉上独特体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701330/extras/f34605c0a5632d03fefba3dec80051cb.poster.avif?t=1755784339\" width=500 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701330/extras/f34605c0a5632d03fefba3dec80051cb.webm?t=1755784339\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701330/extras/f34605c0a5632d03fefba3dec80051cb.mp4?t=1755784339\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701330/extras/8f5a76cba4c527032b77f40cd1f7f453.poster.avif?t=1755784339\" width=296 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701330/extras/8f5a76cba4c527032b77f40cd1f7f453.webm?t=1755784339\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701330/extras/8f5a76cba4c527032b77f40cd1f7f453.mp4?t=1755784339\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>起初您只需为一个原子规划路线，但若以为一切都如此轻松那就大错特错了。随着游戏进程不断推进、挑战难度不断攀升，您将了解和应用新的规则与机制，需要同屏同时调动多个分子，仔细谋划、反复考量路线旁的空间。在解谜的过程中，您原本的规划将不可避免地落空，破题之道唯有不断反思、不断尝试、仔细考量前进的方向。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701330/extras/2d16f39218a9989c8707d914d0f7c84c.poster.avif?t=1755784339\" width=312 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701330/extras/2d16f39218a9989c8707d914d0f7c84c.webm?t=1755784339\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701330/extras/2d16f39218a9989c8707d914d0f7c84c.mp4?t=1755784339\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《Sokobond Express》有着精心设计的关卡，颇具深度的玩法，让化学确凿无疑，您无需具备化学知识依然能在此体验化学家的乐趣。游戏体验快乐有趣、顺应直觉、简洁优雅，您大可沉浸其中，徜徉在解谜艺术之中，获得满满的成就感。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>融合了获奖解谜游戏《键合推箱》、《Cosmic Express》的极简续作<br></li><li>解谜过程中，轻松祥和的背景音乐营造禅意氛围<br></li><li>新锐解谜游戏设计师Jose Hernandez创作，著名解谜游戏专业户Draknek &amp; Friends（《怪兽远征》、《Bonfire Peaks》）发行</li></ul>",
